Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.67,0:00:08.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球 太阳系里唯一有生命的行星 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Earth, the only life sustaining planet in our solar system.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.96,0:00:16.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而 纵贯我们世界的整个历史都是行星的出气桶 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Yet throughout its history our world has been a planetary punching bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.21,0:00:19.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任何东西穿越地球的轨道\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Anything that crosses the orbit of Earth
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.09,0:00:22.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都会在一天内轰击地球 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}could one day slam into the Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.87,0:00:29.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这非常的时刻 天体重物漫游在宇宙间 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}At this very moment, violent celestial heavyweights roam the Universe
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.48,0:00:32.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给予地球毁灭性打击的威胁 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and threaten to deal the Earth a knockout blow.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.45,0:00:37.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,力量就象全世界的武器在同一时间爆炸一样 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The power would be like setting off the whole world's armament at one time,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.74,0:00:40.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全世界会面临下一个广岛 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and would be like standing next to Hiroshima all over the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.21,0:00:43.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的一切都将粉碎 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Everything in us will get ripped apart
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.37,0:00:47.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的身躯将会飞进遥远的空间 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and all of your body would fly off to infinity.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.62,0:00:51.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而一些科学家和前宇航员\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}But some scientists and former astronauts
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.04,0:00:54.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有留下来战斗的愿意 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}are not willing to go down without a fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.24,0:00:58.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们在引发世界末日善恶决战之前\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}They're racing to track down these cosmic killers
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.49,0:01:01.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竞相搜索这些宇宙杀手 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}before they trigger Armageddon.
