Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.81,0:31:58.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球联系着太阳将来的功能失调 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Earth relationship with the Sun will become dysfunctional
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.17,0:32:00.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时 我们的太阳母亲的温度会升高 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}when our solar mother really turns up the heat.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.93,0:32:07.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太阳会变得越来越热 是因为她由燃烧氢转为烧氦 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The Sun gets hotter because it's burning hydrogen into helium.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.74,0:32:10.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四个氢原子成为一个氦原子 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Four hydrogen atoms become one helium atom.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.18,0:32:12.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就意味着燃料质子\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}That means there're fuel particles
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.86,0:32:14.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在太阳里面跳舞 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}dancing around inside the Sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.90,0:32:18.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个过程意味着太阳已经把自己\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And that process basically means that the Sun has to get
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.62,0:32:20.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变得更热和更亮 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}hotter and brighter to hold itself up.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.72,0:32:28.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随着太阳核变得更热 它的个头将变得更大 外面的颜色变红 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}As the Sun's core gets hotter its outer part will swell in size and turn red.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.14,0:32:34.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,假如有堆篝火 放上木头点燃它 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}If you have a bonfire, you have all this wood there you built it up,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.91,0:32:38.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,某些情况下没有足够的木头去燃烧 那个东西倒塌 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and at some point enough logs get burnt and that thing collapses
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.17,0:32:41.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会有巨大的火花爆发 产生巨大的光亮 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and you get this huge burst of sparks and it gets much brighter.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.48,0:32:43.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,某种意义来说 这就象太阳现在\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}In a sense it's like that because the Sun is
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.01,0:32:46.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燃烧氢变为氦的过程 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}right now burning hydrogen into helium
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.15,0:32:48.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而氦就象那个灰烬 如果你喜欢…\Nand the helium is the ash of that, if you like…
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.37,0:32:53.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紧接着太阳充分崩塌 灰烬重新燃烧 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And then as the Sun collapses enough the ash relights
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.73,0:32:55.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,氦燃烧成碳 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and the helium burns into carbon.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.03,0:32:58.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是物体真正得到高温的时候 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And that's when things get really hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.50,0:33:03.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时太阳将变成红巨星 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}At this point Sun will expand into a red giant,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.33,0:33:06.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把地球上的所有生命烧成灰烬 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and incinerate most complex life on Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.82,0:33:12.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太阳变成红巨星时 体积膨胀30倍 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}When the Sun becomes a red giant it will grow to 30 times its size
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.32,0:33:16.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以太阳的表面将到达水星的轨道 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}so the surface of the Sun will actually be out beyond the orbit of Mercury.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.88,0:33:21.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太阳的亮度将增长1000倍 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The luminosity of the Sun will grow up by like 1000 times.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.70,0:33:23.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将使地球变得很热 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}That's gonna make the Earth so hot that
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.65,0:33:27.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球的外壳 岩石 泥土…都将融化 \Nthe outer crust, the rocks, the soil part of the Earth… will melt.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.06,0:33:33.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,整个地球将变为火球 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The whole planet would be a glowing ball of lava.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.24,0:33:40.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太阳将煎熬着内部的行星  \NThe Sun will fry the inner planets and…
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.42,0:33:43.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽管太阳会变得更红和更冷 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}even though the Sun will become red and cooler,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.19,0:33:45.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球会变得更热 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}the Earth will become much hotter.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.10,0:33:49.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是留下地球一堆燃烧的灰烬 就象个炭架 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Just leave the Earth a burnt cinder, like a charcoal bricket.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.67,0:33:52.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以对地球上的生命来说是件坏事 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}So that would be bad for life on Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.16,0:33:56.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球的命运据称还没有结束 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And the Earth's alleged fate isn't over.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.13,0:34:00.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为红巨星太阳在压缩成\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}As a red giant the Sun will fluctuate in size
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.46,0:34:03.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白矮星之前体积将会变化 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}before collapsing into a white dwarf.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.77,0:34:08.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巨大的太阳会突然变为\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The Sun, that was huge, suddenly becomes
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.53,0:34:11.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,体积非常小 密度非常大的太阳 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}a Sun that's very small and extremely dense,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.66,0:34:13.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其体积只有地球大小 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}only about the size of the Earth,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.10,0:34:15.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,占据在太阳系的中央 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}sitting down there at the center of our solar system,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.02,0:34:18.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,较之过去非常地微弱 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}very much fainter than it used to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.69,0:34:21.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切开始冷却 那个星球不再\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And everything cools off and then that object is no longer
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.08,0:34:25.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,产生任何能量 所以它也同样变冷 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}generating energy either, so it begins to cool as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.62,0:34:29.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太阳系最后的结局是冰冷的 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The final fate of the solar system will be to cool off and freeze.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.61,0:34:35.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类或许会在另外一个行星上重新布局 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Humans will probably relocate to another planet
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.54,0:34:39.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者在太阳将地球变成雪球前已经灭种 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}or become extinct before the Sun turns Earth into a snowball.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.99,0:34:44.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎样 太阳会很快烘干我们的地球 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}However the Sun may dry up our world much sooner
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.39,0:34:49.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果太阳没在变为红巨星的时候惩罚我们 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}If the Sun doesn't get us at the time of the red giant phase,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.48,0:34:51.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那它就可能更早地惩罚我们 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}it may well get us earlier by
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.82,0:34:56.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在刚变得足够明亮的时候造成海洋蒸发 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}just becoming bright enough to cause the oceans to evaporate.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.53,0:35:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水是我们生命的基本要素 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Water is an essential component for our life
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.20,0:35:04.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以一旦地球失去所有的水 那时毫无疑问\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and so if Earth actually loses all its water then that's another reason why
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.69,0:35:07.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生命将从地球上消失 那也是太阳的过错 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}life might disappear from the Earth, and it would again be the Sun's fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.51,0:35:13.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能会有一些方法为地球争取到死刑的缓期执行 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}There may be ways for Earth to win a stay of execution.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.09,0:35:20.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太阳膨胀时也会开始丢失质量 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}As the Sun is swelling it also begins to lose mass,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.76,0:35:23.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会比现在丢失的快的多 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}much more rapidly than it's losing it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.48,0:35:25.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然如果太阳质量变得越来越小 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And of course if it's getting less massive
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.00,0:35:27.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对地球的控制也会越来越小 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}it has less of a hold on the Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.87,0:35:31.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球会离太阳更远 轨道更大 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The Earth will move further out, into a larger orbit.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.99,0:35:36.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以这是太阳和其热量增长\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And so it's kind of a race between the growing Sun and the growing heat
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.83,0:35:39.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与地球实际运行之间的竞赛 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}from the Sun and the Earth, actually moving,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.16,0:35:42.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道 与火堆相差一点距离 热量就相差许多 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}you know, a little bit away from that fire that's getting too hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.78,0:35:52.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我们地球以某种方式避免了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}If our planet somehow manages to avoid getting
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.50,0:35:54.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太阳的煎熬和冰冻 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}fried or frozen by the Sun,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.51,0:35:58.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将来也日益荒凉 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}its future remains increasingly bleak.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.89,0:36:08.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个地方充满了冒险 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}This place is full of adventure.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.35,0:36:10.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,游戏将你的胃吊到你的喉咙 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Rides that put your stomach up in your throat,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.74,0:36:12.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,物体的碰撞 充满恐慌…\Nthings that collide, scary stuff…
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.21,0:36:16.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很大程度就象围绕太阳运行的行星地球 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}It's a lot like riding around the Sun on planet Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.63,0:36:19.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而当地球遭到打击或物体开始分解时 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}But when Earth gets smacked or when things start come apart,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.93,0:36:21.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,运行实际已经停止 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}the ride could really be over.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.78,0:36:29.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道那是否意味着宇宙的末日 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I don't know that means for the Universe to end,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.30,0:36:34.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我喜欢时间 我生活在时间里 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}because I like time, I live in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.74,0:36:36.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以想象时间的终结是困难的 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}So it's hard to imagine time ending.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.61,0:36:44.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天科学家沉思着我们不可避免的命运 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Today scientists contemplate our inevitable fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.37,0:36:51.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在遥远的将来 地球和整个宇宙 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}In the distant future, the Earth and the entire Universe,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.37,0:36:54.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能面对最后的宇宙妖魔 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}may face the ultimate cosmic monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.65,0:37:08.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有人怀疑地球最致命的敌人就潜伏在星球之中 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}No one suspects that Earth's most lethal enemy lurks amongst the stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.25,0:37:14.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而在将来 没有预先的警告 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}But in the future, and without prior warning
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.05,0:37:19.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宇宙冷酷的收割机将释放最终的决战 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}a cosmic grim reaper will unleash the ultimate Armageddon.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.85,0:37:27.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑暗的魔鬼将拆散整个宇宙 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The dark villain will stretch apart the Universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.15,0:37:30.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星系将四分五裂 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Galaxies themselves will split apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.33,0:37:34.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恒星和行星将打得粉碎 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Stars and planets will tear to shreds.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.53,0:37:40.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终极大灾难事件被称为"大撕裂" \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The ultimate apocalyptic event is being called "The Big Rip".
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.21,0:37:44.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且一旦开始就不会停止 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And when it begins it won't stop
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.71,0:37:48.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到宇宙里的原子和原子核都变成了碎片 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}until every atom and nuclei in the Universe aren't minced meat.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.51,0:37:58.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"大撕裂" 实际上是宇宙的末日 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}"The Big Rip", it really is the end of the Universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.91,0:38:02.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不喜欢我们是聚会上的最后一个 不知是怎么回事 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}It's not like we're the last ones at the party, wondering what's going on
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.45,0:38:04.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除非我们能够做些什么 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and we can go do something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.55,0:38:06.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很喜欢你关掉所有的灯 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}It's really like you've turned off all the lights.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.25,0:38:08.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此时宇宙刚好终结 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And the Universe just ends.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.95,0:38:17.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,创新的物理学家罗伯特·考德威尔和马克·卡米科维斯基\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Innovator physicists Robert Caldwell and Marc Kamionkowski
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.94,0:38:20.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提出一个"大撕裂"的概念 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}proposed a notion of "The Big Rip".
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.94,0:38:24.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个宇宙最终命运的严酷假设 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}A grim hypothesis about the final fate of the Universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.54,0:38:28.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们过去认为的宇宙 正在扩展 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}We use to think that the Universe, which is currently expanding,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.48,0:38:30.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能扩展到最大点 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}can reach a point of maximum expansion.
