Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.48,0:38:39.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且撕裂也同样在发生 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}but rip everything apart as it does so.
