Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.83,0:38:47.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以惊人的越来越快的速度膨胀 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}at an alarming and increasing pace.
