Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.13,0:38:56.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就象星系刑警队那样 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Acting like a galactic vice squad,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.63,0:38:59.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些年轻的科学家搜索着宇宙杀手 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}these young scientists hunt for the cosmic killer.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.43,0:39:05.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们认为一种叫做暗能量的神秘现象\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}They believe a mysterious phenomenon called dark energy
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.60,0:39:07.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能是犯人 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}may be the culprit.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.90,0:39:10.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盘算着暗能量是 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Figuring out what dark energy is,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.93,0:39:14.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能是宇宙学家现在排在第一号的对象 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}is probably the number one goal of cosmologists today.
