Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.03,0:40:28.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,影响宇宙膨胀的气球 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}of the effects of the expansion of the Universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.43,0:40:34.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个气球变得更大 是星系膨胀\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Here's the balloon gets bigger that's the depiction of the
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.23,0:40:35.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的描述 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}expansion of galaxies.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.69,0:40:40.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一个星系 另一个…\NFirst galaxy, another one…
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.89,0:40:45.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-这些是星系…-好了 \N- These are galaxies… - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.29,0:40:48.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-一个在上面 -好 那是我们的家乡 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}- One over there. - Okay. That's our home.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.69,0:40:52.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当宇宙膨胀时 每一个其它的星系都远离我们 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}As the Universe expands every other galaxy gets farther away from us.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.89,0:41:01.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一般的膨胀 各个星系保持着相同的排列 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}In ordinary expansion each galaxy stays the same size.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.50,0:41:03.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是如果有超级加速膨胀 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}But if you have super accelerated expansion,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.60,0:41:06.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这时单个星系会自己膨胀 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}then the galaxies themselves can each expand.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.11,0:41:07.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个发生在这里 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Which is a sort of what happen here.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.31,0:41:11.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你足够快的吹起它 来描述"大撕裂" \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}If I could blow it up fast enough to depict "The Big Rip" then
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.59,0:41:13.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么气球将爆炸 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}the balloon would explode.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.39,0:41:15.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-那个象时空 不可能会…-拿起它 \N- That's like space-time not being able to… - Take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.89,0:41:17.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并即将结束 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And coming to an end.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.79,0:41:19.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们将听到气球砰的一声 一个洞在气球上 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Sound we'll just pop a hole in the balloon.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.99,0:41:23.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是"大撕裂" \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}That's "The Big Rip".
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.10,0:41:28.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按照考德威尔和卡米科维斯基的说法 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}According to Caldwell and Kamionkowski,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.46,0:41:31.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宇宙不存在"大撕裂"的洞 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}the Universe has no hope of surviving "The Big Rip".
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.16,0:41:37.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们甚至进行了这个世界末日的倒计时 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}They've even come up with a countdown to this apocalyptic event.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.86,0:41:40.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"大撕裂" 开始卷起袖子 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}"The Big Rip", kind of rolls up its sleeves
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.87,0:41:43.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逐步层层剥离宇宙 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and progressively takes apart the Universe layer by layer.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.07,0:41:45.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,运作从外往里 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Working from the outside in,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.81,0:41:48.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从较大规模到较小规模 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}going from the larger scales to the smaller scales.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.71,0:41:52.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十亿年撕裂星系团 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}A billion years to pull apart clusters of galaxies,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.01,0:41:57.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后数亿年撕裂星系 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}then hundreds of millions of years to pull apart galaxies themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.51,0:42:00.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接着 下至太阳系这样的规模 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And then, down to the size of the solar system,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.53,0:42:02.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们说有数十万年就够 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}we're talking hundred of thousands of years.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.05,0:42:06.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后撕裂地球会用…\NAnd then to tear apart the Earth itself will take…
Dialogue: 0,0:42:07.10,0:42:08.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不到一个小时 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}less than an hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.00,0:42:12.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于看起来象什么是个奇怪的想法 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}It's kind of interesting to think about what that would look like.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:13.80,0:42:16.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果在得到保护的太空舱里看着事情的发生 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}If I'm in my protective capsule watching things happen,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:16.90,0:42:21.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将会看到朝着我们来的黑暗吞没地球 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I would see the swallow of darkness that starts coming towards us.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.79,0:42:24.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那一点上 不会很久观察到任何星星 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I would no longer, at that point, be able to see any stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:25.79,0:42:28.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球被一层一层地剥离\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The Earth layer by layer would be peeled off
Dialogue: 0,0:42:28.79,0:42:30.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并被抛出 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and ejected away.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:34.49,0:42:38.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的一切 组成我们的分子 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Everything in us, the molecules that hold us together,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.59,0:42:40.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将被撕开 以及…\Nwould get ripped apart and…
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.99,0:42:43.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,组成你身体的每一个原子都将会…\Nevery atom that makes up your body would get…
Dialogue: 0,0:42:43.49,0:42:46.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将会…将会飞入太空 \Nwould get… would fly off to infinity.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.99,0:42:48.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在一个非常短暂的时间里 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}In a very short period of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.19,0:42:55.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸好人类无须失眠度过"大撕裂" \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Fortunately mankind doesn't need to lose sleep over "The Big Rip".
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.29,0:42:59.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,考德威尔和卡米科维斯基估计从现在算起\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Caldwell and Kamionkowski estimate that it will climax
Dialogue: 0,0:42:59.70,0:43:01.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,500亿年进入顶峰 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}fifty billion years from now,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.99,0:43:05.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时宇宙年龄将超过它现在年龄的三倍 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}when the Universe is over three times its current age.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:06.87,0:43:08.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,试图推测真的对我们是个玩笑吗 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}What's really fun for us is to try to figure out
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.05,0:43:11.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实际上无论会发生什么 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}whether this is actually what's going to happen,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.37,0:43:15.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,科学家虚构的情节描述了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}to paint a science fiction scenario
Dialogue: 0,0:43:16.47,0:43:19.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将会发生什么和我们会发生什么 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}of what might happen and to think what might happen to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:26.17,0:43:28.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太空深处的威胁是真的吗？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Deep space threats are real?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:28.87,0:43:31.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太阳会在明天伤害我们吗？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Sun could harm us tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:31.76,0:43:33.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都发生在遥远的将来 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Others in the far future.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.26,0:43:36.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而一件事是确定的 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}But one thing is certain.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:37.36,0:43:40.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有东西会终结地球以及可能整个宇宙 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Something will terminate Earth and probably the entire Universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:40.70,0:43:42.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永远 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Once and for all.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.22,0:43:45.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这只是时间的问题 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}It's only a matter of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:47.12,0:43:48.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有时想想 还是有帮助的 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}It's useful to sometimes think about,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.52,0:43:52.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球上的生命是多么的脆弱 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}how fragile our life is here on Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:52.72,0:43:56.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许我们不会永远在这里 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}That maybe we're not gonna be here for eternity.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:59.22,0:44:00.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许会有希望 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Maybe there's a hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:00.92,0:44:03.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…他们看起来…\NBut… they way it looks…
Dialogue: 0,0:44:03.62,0:44:05.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宇宙刚好结束 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The Universe just ends.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:05.82,0:44:07.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And that's it.
